html
    head 
        meta(charset="utf-8")
    body
        h1 
            a(href="/topic") Server Side javaScript
        ul
            each topic in topics
                li
                    - rid=encodeURIComponent(topic['@rid']);
                    a(href=`/topic/${rid}`)=topic.title
            li 
                a(href="/topic/add") add topic
        artcle
            if topic
                h2=topic.title
                =topic.description
                if topic.author 
                    div='by '+topic.author
                div
                    a(href=`/topic/${encodeURIComponent(topic['@rid'])}/edit`) edit
                    span=" "
                    a(href=`/topic/${encodeURIComponent(topic['@rid'])}/delete`) delete
            else
                h2 Welcome
                | Hello, this is javascript for server.


            